HINTS
-----

It is _really_ recommend to use the tokyocabinet backend and NOT gdbm.

INSTALL INSTRUCTIONS
--------------------
git clone git://github.com/gebi/dirvish-stats.git
cd dirvish-stats
# for tokyocabinet backend you need the tc python module
# it's distributed as submodule and tested with this version
git submodule update --init
cd lib/tc
python setup.py build
python setup.py install

REQUIRED SOFTWARE
-----------------
python 2.4 works, >=2.5 recommend
python-gdbm
# for tokyocabinet
libtokyocabinet-dev
